sentence: how many big cities are in pennsylvania ?
sentence-with-vars: how many big cities are in state0 ?
sql: select count ( city.city_name ) from city where city.state_name = ' pennsylvania ' and city.population > 150000 ;
sql-with-vars: select count ( city.city_name ) from city where city.state_name = ' state0 ' and city.population > number0 ;
